Class Film

java.lang.Object
com.javi.amazonvieweradv.models.Film
Direct Known Subclasses:
Movie, Series
public abstract class Film
extends java.lang.Object

Film

Film is an abstract parent class

This is the base class of the Films family, since it is abstract, you cannot create request. It has the abstract method view() which is mandatory to be implemented to whichever belongs to the family.
